Subject: Flag of the Republic of Buryatia 
To: Shawn
Content:
The flag of the Republic of Buryatia, a federal subject of Russia, is a tricolour consisting of 2:1:1 horizontal bands of blue, white, and yellow with a yellow Mongol symbol on the hoist of the blue band. The ratio of the flag is 1:2. It was adopted on 29 October 1992.
I read the paragraph on http://wikipedia.org
